casebody.data:
TORRES
v.
CONCRETE DESIGNS, INC. 2019-0953 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 30, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On joint notice of resolution of App.R. 26 applications. Stay of proceedings lifted. Appellees shall file either a memorandum in response to jurisdiction or a notice of cross-appeal and memorandum in support of jurisdiction and in response to jurisdiction no later than October 7, 2019. The cause shall otherwise proceed in accordance with the Supreme Court Rules of Practice.
